{"tid":2315191,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2021DSE自修] 有冇自修中文既人想補底上3","createTime":"2020-12-07T05:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T18:30:29.000Z","uid":125535,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a86124a9c20160247a7fb97b239f5aa4850d6ee6","tid":2315191,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 又係我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊有個補底小組比自修中文既巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同樣同英文一樣因為斷腳而入唔到U/asso既case實在太多太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地今次個班照舊就係針對呢個情況嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n形式係每次個半鐘, 老師會同大家著重操考試技巧&amp;框架,務求大家短時間內清楚&amp;盡做攞3嘅條件,當然都會操返卷一二三<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個小組係定位俾lv2或以下既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以係Google Form留低聯絡方法, 會再pm詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/91FqtrDaWc5BiMAW9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F91FqtrDaWc5BiMAW9&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=8b352250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/91FqtrDaWc5BiMAW9</a><br />\n<br />\n日期: 逢星期五 [2020/12/11,18]<br />\n                        [2020/1/8,15,22,29] <br />\n時期: 下午5點 - 6點半<br />\n地點: 荔枝角既社區中心<br />\n人數: 本身已經差唔多成團~ 如果最後太多人報會按各位巴絲需要&amp;情況再處理<br />\n收費: $100/6堂<br />\n<br />\n<strong>截止日期:今次有啲急,星期五就開始第一堂所以星期三就會截止啦~</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"purple\"><br />\n利申: 社福機構舉辦既, 已補貼, 冇賺到大家一分一毫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><strong>利申擔心既巴絲可以起下我底,一直都有幫開自修生</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英文班仲上緊"},{"p